```bash
sudo sh -c 'printf "[Seat:*]\nallow-guest=false\n" >/etc/lightdm/lightdm.conf.d/50-no-guest.conf'
```

To enable guest:

```bash
sudo rm /etc/lightdm/lightdm.conf.d/50-no-guest.conf
```